Download tar ball from kernel.org
Extract and copy man.conf, Makefile to the directory
run Makefile (requires latest mandoct for -I option), with env OS=posix-2013, HTDIR=html
rename the folders from html0p, html1p to html0P, html1P (maybe fix the Makefile)
rename the generated htmls to have P in section names
copy to /usr/local/apropos_web/posix-2013/man
Add _mandb /usr/local/apropos_web/posix-2013/man.db to man.conf
run makemandb with some env variables (check updater.py)


